# shadcn Usage Guidelines

- Import components from `@/components/ui/*`. Do not re-implement primitives.
- Prefer `variant` + `size` over custom classes; keep additional classes minimal.
- Keep inputs controlled; ensure `RadioGroup`, `Tabs`, etc., do not change controlled state mid-lifecycle.
- Use `Separator`, `Badge`, `Card`, `Tabs`, `Accordion` for layout patterns; avoid heavy bespoke CSS.
- Icons from `lucide-react`; keep sizes consistent (`size-4`, `size-5`).

